W3.CSS Simple Text Button 

<!-- Button Bar / Simple -->
<div class="w3-padding-32">
 <div class="w3-btn-bar w3-border w3-show-inline-block">
  <a href="#" class="w3-btn w3-blue w3-hover-light-blue">Button</a>
  <a href="#" class="w3-btn w3-blue w3-hover-light-blue">Button</a>
  <a href="#" class="w3-btn w3-blue w3-hover-light-blue">Button</a>
  <a href="#" class="w3-btn w3-blue w3-hover-light-blue w3-hide-small">Button</a>
 </div>
</div>
-- Classes Used -- 
w3-padding-32             << Sets Padding to 32
w3-btn-bar                << Creates a Button Bar for the Enclosed Buttons
w3-border                 << Creates a Border for the div element
w3-show-inline-block      << Puts all the Blocks in a Line
w3-btn                    << btn class for w3.css
w3-hide-small             << Hides this button on Small devices
w3-blue                   << Give's it's element a blue background
w3-hover-light-blue       << Changes the BG when u hover to light blue



